nhc_headline: ...HENRIETTE FORECAST TO REGAIN TROPICAL STORM STRENGTH THIS WEEKEND...
summary: ...HENRIETTE FORECAST TO REGAIN TROPICAL STORM STRENGTH THIS WEEKEND... As of 5:00 PM HST Fri Aug 08 the center of Henriette was located near 20.2, -144.6 with movement WNW at 16 mph. The minimum central pressure was 1009 mb with maximum sustained winds of about 35 mph.
